 language: en-US; mso-color-index: 1\">. </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-color-index: 1\">그런 경우에는 골반</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-color-index: 1\">, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-color-index: 1\">허리까지 같이 치료를 해줘야 교정이 되겠지요</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-color-index: 1\">. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-color-index: 1\"></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; unicode-bidi: embed; DIRECTION: ltr; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; MARGIN-LEFT: 0in; language: ko; mso-line-break-override: none; punctuation-wrap: hanging\"><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-color-index: 1\">뼈와 관절, 그리고 주변의 근육과 힘줄을 교정해주는 이수한의원의 추나교정치료는</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-A